    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> and cover them with the <strong>BBQ hoisin sauce</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 30-35 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
