    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into chips</p><p>Add the <strong>chips</strong> to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and put the tray in the oven for 25-30 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
