    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once everything's done, remove the<strong> BBQ hoisin chicken</strong> from the oven</p><p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s] </strong>in half</p><p>Add the<strong> brioche halves</strong> to a baking tray, cut-side down and put the tray in the oven for 3-4 min or until warmed through</p>",
