    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>cooked chicken</strong> to a clean board and shred it apart, using two forks – this technique is known as pulling</p><p>Return the <strong>pulled chicken</strong> to the dish and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> pulled BBQ hoisin chicken</strong></p>",
